Who Do You Think You Are? US - Season 7, Episode 4




Into the Archives

Who Do You Think You Are? digs into its archives and features highlights throughout the seasons including triumphs and tragedies, delightful discoveries and sobering moments. This special episode also unveils outtakes and never-before-seen footage from the vault.
